Package mms.view

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IAbstractView
    Interface that extends interface of the listener for the views.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractView
    Abstract class that implements the interface IAbstractView and the common methods of the view.
    CreditsView
    Class that shows the credits of the program.
    DetailsFilmView
    This class shows the details of the selected film.
    EditablePersonView
    Class used to create a new user/actor or to edit a registered user/actor .
    FeedbackView
    This class creates a view to send a message if there are problem with the program.
    LoginView
    This class creates the start view of the program.
    MenuView
    This class is used to create the menu of customer, admin or society.
    ReviewView
    Show the review of the film.
